    "body": "This PR adds a fused function, `T_exp_T_lim!`, which will allow us to fuse the dss calls in the ClimaAtmos `T_exp!` and `T_lim!` functions, reducing the number of `cuStreamSyncrhonize`s.\r\n\r\nI've also removed the `comms_context`, since this can theoretically be done by users, and reducing the DSS calls has a higher theoretical performance ceiling.\r\n\r\nSince `comms_context` is a very recent feature, and I don't think anybody is using it yet, I've updated the code such that this can be a patch release.",
